\textbf{Inputs}

\begin{itemize}
\item \texttt{y}: Noisy signal


\item \texttt{alg}: Denoising method

\begin{itemize}
\item \texttt{BayesDenoising}: Bayesian Regularization denoising method (to be implemented)


\item \texttt{GCVDenoising}: GCV denoising method


